The '''London Symphony Orchestra''' ('''LSO''') is a [[Wikipedia:United Kingdom|British]] [[symphony]] [[orchestra]] based in [[Wikipedia:London|London]], [[Wikipedia:England|England]] and founded in [[1900s|1904]].<ref name="About us" /> They performed for the film [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="Ben Burtr">{{SW|url=news/jedi-at-40-ben-burtt-randy-thom|text=''Jedi'' at 40 &#124; Ben Burtt and Randy Thom on Crafting Ewokese, Jabba's Voice, and the Rancor's Roar}}</ref>

